N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 9978.7 - Notice of subjects of requests for public inspection

State Regulations

Any person who wishes to know if he or she has been the
subject of a request for public inspection may request from the commission
notification of whether such a request has been filed. That notification shall
not indicate by whom the request was made. Notes
